description: If the smoky goodness of flame-grilled chicken straight off the grill is what you love then have I got the truck for you! Grill Chasers has got wings, wraps, and skewers for all occasions; whether you're stopping by on your lunch or  need to cater that special occasion. Nothing goes better to top off all that delicious flavor than our delicious Chaser BBQ and dipping sauces.
name: Grill Chasers
